OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FTurning very hot and humid at the
OL,7,Fstart of next week with warm and muggy
OL,8,Fnights. Largely dry with strong
OL,9,Fsunshine and just a small chance of a
OL,10,Ffew showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
